result.title: What are these contests??
result.content:
I have recently subscribed to a telegram bot that sends me messages for the future contests on codeforces, codechef and topcoder.

I found some contests which don't appear on the "Contest" tab but showing that they will start in a day or an hour. And also I cant register for those. What are they? The links to the contests are below:
http://codeforces.com/contests/769
http://codeforces.com/contests/780
